       <h2>Sign in to <strong>Gravatar</strong> with WordPress.com Connect</h2> 
       <p><strong>Gravatar now allows you to use a WordPress.com account to sign in. If you have a WordPress.com account already then you can use that, or you can <a href="/connect/?source=_signup" class="wpcc-signup">create a new one</a>.</strong></p> 
       <p style="border-top: dotted 2px #EEE; border-bottom: dotted 2px #EEE; padding: 30px 0; margin: 30px 0;"> <a class="wpcc-button" href="https://en.gravatar.com/connect/" id="wpcc-button">Sign in with <strong>WordPress.com</strong></a> </p> 
       <p>You can also log in at WordPress.com using your old Gravatar account details.</p> 
       <p>If you need a new account, you can <a href="/connect/?source=_signup" class="wpcc-signup">sign up for free</a> at WordPress.com.</p> 
